    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless paintwork and immaculate interior to the perfectly tuned engine, has been maintained to the highest possible standard. There are no mechanical issues, leaks, or cosmetic blemishes to report; the transmission shifts seamlessly, and all electronic features function perfectly. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who demands a vehicle in collector-grade condition without any compromises.",
