      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to an exacting standard. This vehicle displays in showroom condition, featuring an unblemished exterior and a cabin that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle of peerless preservation and provenance.",
