    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014it\u2019s been my pride and joy and looks just as good as the day I bought it! It drives like a total dream and has been pampered since day one. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels practically brand new and turns heads everywhere it goes, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat!",
