    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This unit showcases exceptional mechanical integrity with a factory-spec 6-speed Getrag transmission and a 3.62:1 limited-slip differential. The high-revving inline-six benefits from recent preventative rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the powerband. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and original bushings. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic with an immaculate interior, this example retains its original factory tolerances and provides a visceral, analog driving experience free of any deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Mint condition. Low miles. Garage kept. Original paint. Flawless interior. Non-smoker. No accidents.",
