    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a verified time capsule, preserved in breathtaking showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like factory finish entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with an open-checkbook policy. All original manuals, keys, and a comprehensive service dossier are included. This is not merely a used car, but a collector-grade example that satisfies the most discerning eye. I welcome and encourage independent third-party inspections to confirm its exceptional state.",
